
# Remine_India

It is a E-waste & Li-battery Recycling company Website
that provide company details and provide  services like send a request to pickup raw material from user's organization.
URL
https://rajmaurya95.github.io/remine_india/

- Live previews

- Available Online
- User Friendly

## Deployment

To deploy this project run

```bash
  npm run deploy
```


## Installation

Install my-project with npm

```bash
  npm install my-project
  cd my-project
```
    
## Run Locally

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://link-to-project
```

Go to the project directory

```bash
  cd my-project
```

Install dependencies

```bash
  npm install
```

Start the server

```bash
  npm run start
```


## Running Tests

To run tests, run the following command

```bash
  npm run test
```
